    "Birthday Messages":{
        "Child": ["Dear little one, you're like a sprouting seed, filled with boundless energy and ",
        "curiosity. Each day brings new wonders to explore and lessons to learn. Embrace this time of ",
        "innocence and joy, for it lays the foundation for the adventures yet to come."],
        
        "Adolescent": ["Ah, young adventurer, you stand at the threshold of discovery, caught between ",
        "the worlds of childhood and adulthood. Your body surges with vitality, your mind thirsts for ",
        "knowledge, and your heart yearns for freedom. Embrace the challenges ahead, for they shall ",
        "forge you into the hero you're destined to become."],
        
        "Young Adult": ["Brave soul, you tread the path of independence and ambition, your spirit ",
        "ablaze with passion and purpose. Every decision you make shapes your destiny, every experience ",
        "molds your character. Embrace the journey, for it is yours to shape and conquer."],
        
        "Middle Age": ["Wise traveler, you've journeyed through the peaks and valleys of life, ",
        "weathering storms and basking in moments of calm. Your strength lies not only in your physical ",
        "prowess but also in the depth of your wisdom. Embrace the balance between duty and desire, for ",
        "it is the hallmark of a seasoned adventurer."],
        
        "Elder": ["Seasoned sage, you've witnessed the passing of seasons and the turning of tides, ", 
        "your spirit tempered by the trials of time. Your legacy echoes in the hearts of those you've ",
        "touched, your counsel sought by the young and old alike. Embrace the tranquility of reflection, ",
        "for it unveils the true richness of your journey."],
        
        "Venerable": ["Ancient one, you stand as a beacon of wisdom and resilience, your spirit endures ", 
        "like the roots of an ancient tree. While your body is not as spry as it once was, each of your ",
        "wrinkles tells a story, and each scar a testament to your indomitable spirit. Embrace the ", 
        "tranquility of the twilight years, for it is a time of profound introspection and the sharing ",
        "of your timeless wisdom."]
    },

